{#
RULES: This should be sent upon Hospital Profile submission/creation. Sent to account owner.
Assumptions: No Clinics, No Dr profiles nor any public info have yet to be added to the database.
Auto-notification subject line: #Hospital_Name# has been added to {{ site_name }}
Auto-notification From address: support@healthcareabroad.com
#}
{% block subject %}
    {% autoescape false %}
{{ institution_name }} has been added to {{ site_name }}
    {% endautoescape %}
{% endblock %}

{% block body_text %}
    {% autoescape false %}

Thank you for creating a profile for {{ institution_name }} on {{ site_name }}!

The next step for patients to find you on {{ site_name }} is to get your hospital’s clinics listed in our international directory.

To make sure that they find complete and relevant information about everything that you have to offer, we suggest that you:

Continue the submission process to add all the clinics/centers within your hospital {{ url.add_centers }}
Create profiles for the Doctors within the clinics {{ url.feature_doctors }}
List the treatments and specializations for each clinic {{ url.list_treatments }}
Post photos and videos of your clinics {{ url.upload_photos }}
List contact details for prospective patients to contact you {{ url.contact_info }}

Need help?  Contact Support at {{ email.support }} or visit {{ url.support }}.

All the best,

The {{ site_name }} Team

    {% endautoescape %}
{% endblock %}

